                                <div class="post-image">
                                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549366021-9f761d450615?w=800&q=80"
                                        alt="African Wildlife">
                                    <div class="category-tag">Environment</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="post-content">
                                    <h3>Guardians of the Savannah</h3>
                                    <p>How local communities are leading conservation efforts in East Africa's wildlife
                                        corridors...</p>
                                    <div class="post-meta">
                                        <div class="author">
                                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=100&q=80"
